/g>\n      </svg>\n      <span>Scroll to Enter</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>","<section class=\"chapter\" id=\"fabric\" style=\"--acc:#FFDD00\">\n  <div class=\"frame chapter-body\">\n    <div class=\"split\">\n      <div>\n        <div class=\"eyebrow rv\"><b>Platform Architecture</b> One Source of Truth</div>\n        <h2 class=\"display-lg rv rv-d1\">Composable products.<br><span class=\"accent\">One intelligence core.</span></h2>\n        <p class=\"lede rv rv-d2\" style=\"margin-top:26px\">Most software portfolios are silos wearing shared branding. MoxSuite is engineered differently: a single governed data foundation and a shared AI core underpin every product. Verify a contact once — the entire platform knows. Close a deal anywhere — finance already sees it.</p>\n        <div class=\"mox-cap rv rv-d3\" style=\"justify-content:flex-start;margin-top:32px\">\n          <span><b>◆</b>&nbsp; Governed Data Foundation</span>\n          <span><b>◆</b>&nbsp; Shared AI Core</span>\n          <span><b>◆</b>&nbsp; Unified Commercials</span>\n          <span><b>◆</b>&nbsp; Single Sign-On</span>\n          <span><b>◆</b>&nbsp; Multi-Tenant by Design</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"glass rv rv-d2\" style=\"padding:26px\">\n        <div class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"margin-bottom:10px\"><b>Live Topology</b> Core → Portfolio</div>\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 460 470\" style=\"width:100%;height:auto\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n          <defs><linearGradient id=\"axG\" x1=\"0\" x2=\"1\"><stop offset=\"0\" stop-color=\"#FFDD00\"/><stop offset=\"1\" stop-color=\"#FF810F\"/></linearGradient></defs>\n          <circle cx=\"230\" cy=\"230\" r=\"178\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,.1)\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n          <circle cx=\"230\" cy=\"230\" r=\"112\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"rgba(255,221,0,.26)\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"4 8\">\n            <animateTransform attributeName=\"transform\" type=\"rotate\" values=\"0 230 230;360 230