></i><i class=\"dim\" style=\"--i:31\"></i><i class=\"dim\" style=\"--i:32\"></i><i class=\"dim\" style=\"--i:33\"></i><i class=\"dim\" style=\"--i:34\"></i></div>\n      <div class=\"map-legend\">\n        <span><b>●</b>&nbsp; Live / In Build — 8</span>\n        <span style=\"color:rgba(245,244,248,.45)\">○&nbsp; Roadmap — 27 to come</span>\n        <span><b>◆</b>&nbsp; Revenue · Finance · Operations · Industry Platforms</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>","<section class=\"chapter\" id=\"mxcontact\" style=\"--acc:#FFDD00\">\n  <div class=\"frame chapter-body\">\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;max-width:860px;margin:0 auto 60px\">\n      <div class=\"eyebrow rv\" style=\"justify-content:center\"><b>Get In</b> Early Access &amp; Partnerships</div>\n      <h2 class=\"display-xl rv rv-d1\" style=\"font-size:clamp(38px,6vw,96px)\">Plug into<br><span class=\"accent\">the platform.</span></h2>\n      <p class=\"lede rv rv-d2\" style=\"margin:26px auto 0\">Early access, pilots, reseller partnerships or a walkthrough of any product — tell us where you fit and we'll come back within one business day.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"glass contact-card rv rv-d3\">\n      <div>\n        <h3 class=\"display-md\" style=\"margin-bottom:14px\">Request access</h3>\n        <p class=\"thin\" style=\"font-size:14px;max-width:52ch\">Pick the areas you care about. We'll respond with a live demo, pilot pricing and the integration path into the shared core.</p>\n        <div class=\"contact-list\" style=\"margin-top:32px\">\n          <div class=\"row\"><span class=\"k\">Email</span><span>info@easehawk.com</span></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"k\">Call</span><span><a href=\"tel:+17622787611\" style=\"color:inherit;text-decoration:none\">+1 762 278 7611</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href=\"tel:+919958478569\" style=\"color:inherit;text-decoration:none\">+91 99584 78569</a></span></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"k\">Book a Call</span><span><a href=\"https://calendly.com/easehawk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color:var(--signal);text-decoration:none\">calendly.com/easehawk ↗</a></span></div>\n          <div class=\"row\"><span class=\"k\">Suite Domain</span><span>moxsend.ai</span></div>\n          <div class=\"row\"><span class=\"k\">Built By</span><span>EaseHawk · WeWork DLF Forum, Cybercity, Gurugram, India</span></div>\n          <div class=\"row\"><span class=\"k\">Social</span><span><a class=\"soc\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/easehawk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.225 0z\"/></svg>EaseHawk Technologies</a></span></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <form id=\"reqForm\" novalidate>\n        <div class=\"f-grid\">\n          <label class=\"f-field\"><span>Full name *</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" required placeholder=\"Your name\"></label>\n          <label class=\"f-field\"><span>Work email *</span><input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" required placeholder=\"name@company.com\"></label>\n          <label class=\"f-field\"><span>Company</span><input type=\"text\" name=\"company\" placeholder=\"Organisation\"></label>\n          <label class=\"f-field\"><span>Region</span>\n            <select name=\"region\"><option>UAE</option><option>Saudi Arabia</option><option>Qatar</option><option>USA</option><option>Canada</option><option>India</option><option>Other</option></select>\n          </label>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"f-field\" style=\"margin-top:16px\"><span>Area of interest — pick any</span>\n          <div class=\"f-chips\" id=\"needChips\">\n            <button type=\"button\">AI Outreach Suite</button>\n            <button type=\"button\">Revenue &amp; CRM</button>\n            <button type=\"button\">Quoting &amp; Proposals</button>\n            <button type=\"button\">Finance &amp; Forecasting</button>\n            <button type=\"button\">Education Platform</button>\n            <button type=\"button\">Automotive Platform</button>\n            <button type=\"button\">Full Ecosystem</button>\n            <button type=\"button\">Partnership / Reseller</button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"f-grid\" style=\"margin-top:16px\">\n          <label class=\"f-field\"><span>I am a</span>\n            <select name=\"timeline\"><option>Business buyer</option><option>School / Institution</option><option>Dealership / Rental group</option><option>Reseller / Partner</option><option>Investor</option><option>Just exploring</option></select>\n          </label>\n          <label class=\"f-field\"><span>Team size</span>\n            <select name=\"budget\"><option>1 – 10</option><option>11 – 50</option><option>51 – 200</option><option>200+</option></select>\n          </label>\n        </div>\n        <label class=\"f-field\" style=\"margin-top:16px\"><span>Anything else?</span>\n          <textarea name=\"message\" rows=\"4\" placeholder=\"What are you trying to solve?\"></textarea>\n        </label>\n        <button class=\"cta\" type=\"submit\" style=\"margin-top:24px;width:100%;text-align:center;justify-content:center\"><span>Request access</span></button>\n        <p class=\"f-note\" id=\"formNote\">Your request opens in your email client, pre-addressed to the MoxSuite team.</p>\n      </form>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>"]